						<summary>

						<p>This is also probably a record of Uttama-Chōḷa and registers a similar gift by Śōlaipirāṉ-Kramavittaṉ of the <hi rend="italic">gōṭṭam</hi> (<hi rend="italic">gōshṭha</hi>-assembly) of Paṇḍitavatsalachchēri, who left it in charge of the <hi rend="italic">maṉṟāḍikkalanai</hi> for burning a perpetual lamp.</p>						

						</summary>
